OL,3,CUS influencer Nara Smith says two-year-
OL,4,Cold daughter is in remission
OL,6,FSocial media star Nara Smith has said
OL,7,Fher two-year-old daughter Whimsy is in
OL,8,Fremission after being diagnosed with
OL,9,Fcancer.
OL,11,FThe "trad-wife" influencer is best
OL,12,Fknown for narrating parts of her day
OL,13,Fin a low voice and making meals from
OL,14,Fscratch while wearing extravagant
OL,15,Fclothes.
OL,17,FIt comes weeks after the 24-year-old,
OL,18,Fwho is married to model Lucky Blue
OL,19,FSmith, revealed that their daughter
OL,20,Fhad undergone chemotherapy since she
OL,21,Fwas diagnosed last year.
OL,26,@sD@EOUsD@OO]
