OL,3,CUS influencer Nara Smith says two-year-
OL,4,Cold daughter is in remission
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn a video shared on Instagram, Smith
OL,12,Fsaid: "(We) wanted to wait until she
OL,13,Fwas done with treatment and us knowing
OL,14,Fwhat the outcome of her situation
OL,15,Fwould be before sharing it, and even
OL,16,Ffinding the words to share it.
OL,18,F"Now that she's finally in remission,
OL,19,Fit felt like I could find the words to
OL,20,Fshare.
OL,26,@tD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
