OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1784402279
OL,3,CUS influencer Nara Smith says two-year-
OL,4,Cold daughter is in remission
OL,6,F"The whole point of me sharing our
OL,7,Fexperience was to shed light on what
OL,8,Fso many families go through and battle
OL,9,Fprivately.
OL,11,F"Going through chemo treatments opened
OL,12,Fmy eyes to how expensive medical care
OL,13,Fis, and what a toll it takes on
OL,14,Ffamilies specifically."
OL,16,FSmith said she and her husband, 28,
OL,17,Fhave been trying to "return to
OL,18,Feveryday life", adding that they are
OL,19,Ftaking it "day by day".
