OL,3,CUS influencer Nara Smith says two-year-
OL,4,Cold daughter is in remission
OL,6,F"I don't know whether life will ever
OL,7,Ffeel normal again, but we're trying to
OL,8,Fnavigate this next chapter the best
OL,9,Fthat we can," she added.
OL,11,FSmith went on to thank people for
OL,12,Ftheir "kind messages, prayers, and
OL,13,Fsupport" and shared her support for
OL,14,Ffamilies that "are actively still
OL,15,Fgoing through this fight".
